Padding¶

In [19]:
threshold = 2
total = len(tokenizer.word_index) 
rare = 0 
total_ = 0 
rare_ = 0 


for key, value in tokenizer.word_counts.items():
    total_ = total_ + value

    if(value < threshold):
        rare = rare + 1
        rare_ = rare_ + value

print('   :',total)
print(' %s    : %s'%(threshold - 1, rare))
print("   :", (rare / total)*100)
print("     :", (rare_ / total_)*100)

In [29]:
def under(max_len, list):
    a = 0
    for s in list:
        if(len(s) <= max_len):
            a = a + 1
    print(' %s  : %s'%(max_len, (a / len(list))*100))

LSTM¶

In [34]:
from tensorflow.keras.layers import Embedding, Dense, LSTM,Dropout
from tensorflow.keras.models import Sequential
from tensorflow.keras.models import load_model
from tensorflow.keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping
In [55]:
model = Sequential()
model.add(Embedding(size, 100))
model.add(LSTM(64))
Dropout(0.5)
model.add(Dense(32))
model.add(Dense(9, activation='softmax'))
In [56]:
early = EarlyStopping(monitor='val_loss', mode='min', verbose=1, patience=3)
In [57]:
model.compile(optimizer='rmsprop', loss='sparse_categorical_crossentropy', metrics=['acc'])
history = model.fit(X_train, Y_train, epochs=10, callbacks=[early], batch_size=10, validation_split=0.2)

fig, loss_ax = plt.subplots()

acc_ax = loss_ax.twinx()

loss_ax.plot(history.history['loss'], 'y', label='train loss')

acc_ax.plot(history.history['val_acc'], 'g', label='val acc')
